{"tid":1494392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話唔分和理非同勇武個啲全部同我入嚟！！！","createTime":"2019-08-21T15:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T17:34:44.000Z","uid":12425,"like":32,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed938e8cb7d1c6f8b8a9f3e9ff3fddc7ab72dce","tid":1494392,"uid":12425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"又話唔分化唔割席！<br />\n點解我無乜gear就要比人屌走<br />\n你full fear係咪代表你係勇武 你可以保護我？<br />\n頭先有個女仔仲瘦弱過我 屌我走 話保護我<br />\n我心諗你憑乜保護我？ 係咪有gear就大曬？ <br />\n我小你一個頭盔我係咪就唔可以出嚟抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n呢個問題一直存在 次次都叫無gear嘅快啲走<br />\n我唔見得齊曬裝個啲人好勇武好可以保護到自己<br />\n我想講心態有時候係大過gear<br />\n我出過嚟咁多次好可以衡量到自己承受到咩傷害 咩時候要走 <br />\n有時齊裝嘅人仲驚撚過我 (見識過好多次）<br />\n唔該唔好再叫人走走走 一切由自己決定！<br />\n<br />\n最後，不分化不割席！<br />\n唔該唔好再屌9和理非要人走！ 我可能仲勇武過你！"},{"pid":"37bac09934bf5d5c6f3dab886c65f6dbc0f8983f","tid":1494392,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:35:02.000Z","msg":"元朗 @2330 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/mid/2954daee821566401269486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2Fmid%2F2954daee821566401269486&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn0%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=7072a7c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/mid/2954daee821566401269486</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fAKvgMD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAKvgMD.png&h=da708c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能 HKmap.live<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"77e5f247cc3c0a76ee0f608ecdb103d9687931e0","tid":1494392,"uid":12425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:35:21.000Z","msg":"自推到你地入嚟屌9我為止！"},{"pid":"00e8d9d7e3a8c4b282739c03f3bcbf6cac516ff9","tid":1494392,"uid":12425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"自推到你地入嚟屌9我為止！"},{"pid":"e95cbdf277a5bc3f83c011b68ee3fdf68f394066","tid